extendedInfo.description: Download for FREE Now!!WHAT IS "Headset Icon" ? "HeadsetIcon" detects your headset "plug in" or "plug out",it could set the volume by auto and show COOL notification & headset manufacture logo!THIS APP WILL NOT CHANGE EQ, BUT WILL ADD IN THE FUTURE!!Functions:1.Customized your own notification text!!2.User can choose any app on notification to start!(New)3."Auto Volume" function.4.No root required.5.Show icon with out plugging in your headset.(experimental,user should turn of this in setting and click the image to disable icons.)-HOW TO USE: 1.Start the HeadsetIcon App. 2.Simply click the image to "Enable" ! 4.PLUG YOUR EARPHONES NOW!!!try it!-HOW TO DISABLE: 1.Start the HeadsetIcon App. 2.Simply click any image to "Disable"! 3.Text will show "Disabled".-HOW TO USE AUTO VOLUME: 1.Check the Auto Volume checkbox.2.User needs to set the volume for the first time.3.DONE! Plug in your headset and try it!-[NEW] HOW TO USE CUSTOMIZED NOTIFICATION:1.Press Menu and go to Settings.2.Write down your own text! anything you want!3.You must Enable HeadsetService to show customized notification.Permission explanation:RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED --> Open HeadsetIcon when boot completeINTERNET  --> You can share with your Facebook friends by pressing the LIKE buttonACCESS_NETWORK_STATE --> Check network status*HeadsetIcon will run in the background! *Please DON'T play with your headphone jack by plugging then unplugging, because we DON'T GUARANTEE your headphone jack!*The HeadsetIcon application is ONLY FOR FUN, there is NO COMMERCIAL purposes.*Have fun and SHARE with your friends!Icons :1.1.0akgaudiotechnicabeatsbeyerdynamicearsonicsgradologitechpanasonic(will remove because the graphic isn't good)philipssennheisersomicsonyultrasone1.1.2Walkman (Sony is too small)DenonAndroid ICS system headset icon1.1.3EtymoticUltimate Ears1.1.4FCC(Federal Communications Commission) (Fun!)JAYSSOULKlipsch1.1.5Better looking Denon icon.1.1.7TDKNuForceRazerDobly1.1.8JVCKoss1.1.9BoseWestoneSony1.1.10SkullcandyV-MODA1.1.11AppleMarshallMunitioShure(1930 logo)WeSC1.1.12CreativeRazorPhillipsSoundmagicMEEMonopriceSol Republic...more coming soon,we take requests!If you got some error after updating, contact us,and uninstall the application then reinstall again.Some users using Xperia encounter a "Device Unsupported" problem.This problem is a kernel problem that can't fix by "Headset Icon",if you want to make "Headset Icon"  function well,please use supported headset,thank you!If user can't see the image gallery in the middle at the first time user run the app ,check the "Auto Volume" checkbox ,or restart the app to fix this!Using the customize rom might effect the function."Using a customize rom might cause the application not work properly! please contact developer."'IMPORTANT: THIS APP DOES'NT HAVE EQ!
